    public class MicroSimTreeBuilder
extends org.ascape.runtime.swing.navigator.DefaultTreeBuilder
    TreeBuilder that creates MicroSimScapeNode for MicroSimScape model elements, provides a PeformActionOnSelectedNode selection listener and same as DefaultTreeBuilder for everything else.
